---
Title: Mumonkan - Ordinary Mind is the Way
Source:
  - Title: The Teachings of the Buddha
    Translator: Sumiko Kudo
    Page: 206
    ISBN: 1-57062-124-1
    LOCN: BQ915.T43 1995
    Editor: Jack Kornfield
---
Hundreds of flowers in spring, the moon in autumn,
A cool breeze in summer, and snow in winter;
if there is no vain cloud in your mind
For you it is a good season.
